  image(images.at("figure-27-2").path, width: 80%),
  caption: images.at("figure-27-2").caption
)

#figure(
  image(images.at("figure-27-3").path, width: 80%),
  caption: images.at("figure-27-3").caption
)

- *Flightlessness*: Evolved independently in many groups (e.g., penguins, ostriches), often on islands lacking predators.
  - Associated with loss of keel on sternum and heavy flight muscles.

