== Skeleton
- *Pneumatized bones*: Light, delicate, laced with air cavities, yet strong.
- *Skull*: Diapsid (modified), fused into one piece, large braincase and orbits. Toothless keratinized beak.
- *Rigidity*: Fused vertebrae (*synsacrum*, *pygostyle*), ribs with *uncinate processes*.
- *Sternum*: Bears a large *keel* for flight muscle attachment.
- *Furcula*: Fused clavicles (wishbone), stores energy during wing beats.

