== Muscular System
- *Pectoralis*: Depresses wing (power stroke).
- *Supracoracoideus*: Raises wing; positioned on breast (low center of gravity), pulls via tendon over shoulder ("rope-and-pulley").
- *Leg Muscles*: Concentrated in thigh; tendons extend to toes (prevents freezing, lightweight feet).
- *Toe-locking mechanism*: Automatically grips perch when settling.

